      "section_index": 0,
      "section_kind": "weather_opening",
      "segments": [
        "s0"
      ],
      "start": 9.93,
      "text": "It is currently a clear morning in Berlin-Tempelhof with a temperature of 30 degrees."
    },
    {
      "end": 18.71,
      "id": "p1",
      "index": 1,
      "section_index": 1,
      "section_kind": "news_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s1"
      ],
      "start": 16.61,
      "text": "With the morning weather set, here is the news."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "a9a39810836"
      ],
      "end": 32.91,
      "id": "p2",
      "index": 2,
      "section_index": 2,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s2",
        "s3"
      ],
      "start": 19.03,
      "text": "Google DeepMind has integrated computer use as a built-in tool for Gemini 3.5 Flash. This update allows developers to build agents that can interact directly across different software platforms."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "a3253e53b80",
        "a2f4d7fa2ad"
      ],
      "end": 52.99,
      "id": "p3",
      "index": 3,
      "section_index": 3,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s4",
        "s5"
      ],
      "start": 34.25,
      "text": "While Gemini moves toward software agency, NVIDIA is focusing on the hardware and libraries needed for physical and specialized AI. The company is accelerating Bird's-Eye-View perception on its GPUs to improve how autonomous vehicles and robotics project camera data into a top-down grid."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "a2f4d7fa2ad"
      ],
      "end": 72.28,
      "id": "p4",
      "index": 4,
      "section_index": 4,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s6",
        "s7"
      ],
      "start": 53.99,
      "text": "NVIDIA is also using the NeMo AutoModel open library to speed up the fine-tuning of Transformers. This system leverages Mixture of Experts foundations, including distributed execution and dynamic weight loading, to reduce the compute cost of deploying custom generative AI."
    },
    {
      "end": 75.12,
      "id": "p5",
      "index": 5,
      "section_index": 5,
      "section_kind": "weather_return_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s8"
      ],
      "start": 72.66,
      "text": "After the headlines, back to the weather."
    },
    {
      "end": 80.58,
      "id": "p6",
      "index": 6,
      "section_index": 6,
      "section_kind": "weather_closing",
      "segments": [
        "s9"
      ],
      "start": 75.3,
      "text": "This afternoon will remain clear with temperatures between 29 and 33 degrees."
    },
    {
      "end": 84.74,
      "id": "p7",
      "index": 7,
      "section_index": 7,
      "section_kind": "closing",
      "segments": [
        "s10"
      ],
      "start": 81.56,
      "text": "And that's it for your personal morning broadcast."
    },
    {
      "end": 90.76,
      "id": "p8",
      "index": 8,
      "section_index": 8,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
        "s11"
      ],
      "start": 88.54,
      "text": "[mature adult voice, intensely emotional, tender, radiant; hold a long breath after Rise] Rise... and shine."
    },
    {
      "end": 91.26,
      "id": "p9",
      "index": 9,
      "section_index": 8,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
        "s12"
      ],
      "start": 90.76,
      "text": "[very very long pause before speaking; then mature adult voice, most emotional, strong, warm, radiant, deeply encouraging; hold a long breath after Rise] Rise... and shine."
    }
  ],
